description:
In this JamSnack, you'll learn what's new in Angular. Stephen Fluin, Dev Advocate for Angular at Google, talks about exciting updates for the project, including a first ever roadmap published, and open source Jamstack tool called Scully, and Angular Universal. 

Learn more about Angular: https://twitter.com/angular , https://angular.io/

Presented by Stephen Fluin, Developer Advocate for Angular, Google, https://twitter.com/stephenfluin, https://fluin.io/

Brought to you by Netlify (netlify.com) - Jamstack Conf Virtual 2020 https://jamstackconf.com
title: JamSnack - What's New in Angular
